Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:10.24,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(582.045,276.783)}{\pos(250,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}詹姆・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}“弑君者” 御林铁卫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:10.57,正文,,0,0,0,,能塞进多少根儿手指啊？\N{\fs16}do you think we could shove up his ass?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.34,正文,,0,0,0,,这可得看他之前有没有练习过\N{\fs16}Depends if he's had any practice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:13.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(392.415,268.614)}{\pos(250,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}布蕾妮・塔斯{\b0}{\fs12}\N“美人” 詹姆的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.34,正文,,0,0,0,,你跟你姐姐搞的时候玩过这种花样吗？ 弑君者？\N{\fs16}Is that the sort of thing you and your sister go in for, Kingslayer?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:21.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(325.683,243.102)}{\pos(480,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:20.11,正文,,0,0,0,,她可曾替我们松过你的菊花？\N{\fs16}She loosened you up for us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.56,正文,,0,0,0,,他要摔下来了\N{\fs16}He's going to fall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.19,正文,,0,0,0,,他要从马上摔下来了 来人帮帮他啊\N{\fs16}He's going to fall off his horse. Someone help him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.27,正文,,0,0,0,,水\N{\fs16}Water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.30,正文,,0,0,0,,水\N{\fs16}Water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.94,正文,,0,0,0,,求求你 水\N{\fs16}Please, water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.47,正文,,0,0,0,,水 水\N{\fs16}Wa-water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:51.14,正文,,0,0,0,,水 求求你\N{\fs16}Water, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.07,正文,,0,0,0,,求求你 求求你\N{\fs16}Please. Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.62,正文,,0,0,0,,如果我死了 你就什么也――\N{\fs16}If I die, you won't be getting--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.08,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 得了吧\N{\fs16}Oh, enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.22,正文,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs16}Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:15.43,正文,,0,0,0,,还真没见过有人连喝马尿都喝的这么带劲呐\N{\fs16}Can't say that I've ever seen a man drink horse piss that fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.72,正文,,0,0,0,,住手！\N{\fs16}Stop!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.03,正文,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fs16}Far enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:28.05,正文,,0,0,0,,胆敢再犯 我就剁了你的另一只手\N{\fs16}Do that again and I'll take your other hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:34.29,正文,,0,0,0,,你进来吧\N{\fs16}Come on, you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.24,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(492.825,279.752)}{\pos(180,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}提利昂・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}“小恶魔” 财政大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.60,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 提利昂大人 进来 进来\N{\fs16}Oh, Lord Tyrion. Come in, come in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.74,正文,,0,0,0,,我希望咱俩能够\N{\fs16}I hope we might speak.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.44,正文,,0,0,0,,推心置腹的谈一谈\N{\fs16}In confidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.38,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 咱不一直都推心置腹的嘛\N{\fs16}Oh, always in confidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.15,正文,,0,0,0,,关于黑水河的那档子事儿\N{\fs16}About the events of the Blackwater.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.15,正文,,0,0,0,,现在谈这个是否有些不合时宜？\N{\fs16}Perhaps this is the wrong time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.05,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 不 我看正合时宜\N{\fs16}Oh, no. It's a wonderful time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.75,正文,,0,0,0,,我觉得没准你的某只小小鸟\N{\fs16}I thought one of your little birds{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.56,正文,,0,0,0,,知道点什么 关于我姐姐图谋……\N{\fs16}might have knowledge of my sister's intentions to--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.06,正文,,0,0,0,,取您性命？\N{\fs16}End your life?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.93,正文,,0,0,0,,虽然我接过了小指头的职位\N{\fs16}I didn't inherit Littlefinger's spies{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.49,正文,,0,0,0,,但他可没把那些耳目眼线一并留给我\N{\fs16}along with his position, I'm afraid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.56,正文,,0,0,0,,所以我只能来找你帮忙\N{\fs16}Which is why I'm coming to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.83,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我需要证据 - 证据？\N{\fs16}- I need proof. - Proof?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.01,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(264.262,226.577)}{\pos(400,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}瓦里斯{\b0}\N{\fs12} “八爪蜘蛛” 情报总管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.27,正文,,0,0,0,,- 还会有审判么？ - 是我想知道而已\N{\fs16}- Will there be a trial? - I need to know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.40,正文,,0,0,0,,她曾对我密语 可我没有别的证据\N{\fs16}I have no proof, only whispers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.01,正文,,0,0,0,,在讨论这些见不得人的东西前\N{\fs16}Before all this nastiness,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:33.61,正文,,0,0,0,,我本想跟你讲讲我是如何被阉的\N{\fs16}I was going to tell you the story of how I was cut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.35,正文,,0,0,0,,你现在还想听么？\N{\fs16}Do you want to hear it still?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.78,正文,,0,0,0,,不知道 我该听么？\N{\fs16}I don't know. Do I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.55,正文,,0,0,0,,当我还是个男孩的时候 我曾跟着一个剧团\N{\fs16}As a boy, I travelled with a troupe of actors{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.55,正文,,0,0,0,,在自由城邦巡演\N{\fs16}through the Free Cities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.36,正文,,0,0,0,,有一天 在密尔\N{\fs16}One day in Myr,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.23,正文,,0,0,0,,一个男人给我的主人开了一个\N{\fs16}a certain man made my master an offer{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.33,正文,,0,0,0,,无法拒绝的高价\N{\fs16}too tempting to refuse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.93,正文,,0,0,0,,我很害怕 担心这男人会怎样对我\N{\fs16}I feared the man meant to use me as I'd heard{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.96,正文,,0,0,0,,他会不会是那种对男童感兴趣的人\N{\fs16}some men used small boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.70,正文,,0,0,0,,然而事实比这更糟\N{\fs16}But what he wanted was far worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.37,正文,,0,0,0,,他对我下了药\N{\fs16}He gave me a potion{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.50,正文,,0,0,0,,那药水让我无法动弹 甚至无法言语\N{\fs16}that made me powerless to move or speak,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.54,正文,,0,0,0,,可它却没有麻痹我的感觉\N{\fs16}yet did nothing to dull my senses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.98,正文,,0,0,0,,他用一柄弯刀 将我的那里连根带梢\N{\fs16}With a hooked blade he sliced me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.95,正文,,0,0,0,,一片一片的切下 然后他伴着咒语\N{\fs16}root and stem, chanting all the while.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:13.58,正文,,0,0,0,,将它们丢入火盆中烧掉\N{\fs16}He burned my parts in a brazier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.15,正文,,0,0,0,,火焰转而变蓝\N{\fs16}The flames turned blue{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.85,正文,,0,0,0,,然后我听到有个声音响应了他的召唤\N{\fs16}and I heard a voice answer his call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:27.36,正文,,0,0,0,,如今我仍会时不时的梦到它――\N{\fs16}I still dream of that night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.83,正文,,0,0,0,,梦到的不是那个巫师\N{\fs16}Not of the sorcerer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.13,正文,,0,0,0,,也不是那把刀\N{\fs16}not of his blade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.60,正文,,0,0,0,,而是那个火焰里的声音\N{\fs16}I dream of the voice from the flames.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.84,正文,,0,0,0,,那是个神祗？ 还是恶魔？\N{\fs16}Was it a god? A demon?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.54,正文,,0,0,0,,又或是魔术师的鬼把戏？\N{\fs16}A conjuror's trick?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.71,正文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs16}I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:44.21,正文,,0,0,0,,但是确实有个声音响应了巫师的召唤\N{\fs16}But the sorcerer called and a voice answered.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.65,正文,,0,0,0,,从那天起\N{\fs16}And ever since that day,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:50.45,正文,,0,0,0,,我开始憎恨一切魔法 和使用它们的人\N{\fs16}I have hated magic and all those who practice it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.89,正文,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我要如此热切的帮助你\N{\fs16}But you can see why I was eager to aid{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:56.29,正文,,0,0,0,,对抗史坦尼斯和他的红袍女祭司\N{\fs16}in your fight against Stannis and his Red Priestess.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:07:00.02,正文,,0,0,0,,这算是某种复仇的象征\N{\fs16}A symbolic revenge of sorts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:04.09,正文,,0,0,0,,是的 嗯… 我急不可耐地要跟那些\N{\fs16}Yes, ahem. I feel the need for actual revenge{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.13,正文,,0,0,0,,想置我于死地的人来一场\N{\fs16}against the actual person{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.66,正文,,0,0,0,,真刀真枪的复仇\N{\fs16}who tried to have me killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:12.03,正文,,0,0,0,,但是这事儿没点影响力可办不到 而这些……\N{\fs16}Which will require a degree of influence, which--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.40,正文,,0,0,0,,恰是你此时此刻\N{\fs16}You do not possess{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.14,正文,,0,0,0,,所不具备的\N{\fs16}at the moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.47,正文,,0,0,0,,说到影响力 我发现这玩意儿\N{\fs16}But influence is largely{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.64,正文,,0,0,0,,实际上就是耐性的较量\N{\fs16}a matter of patience, I have found.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:26.05,正文,,0,0,0,,那巫师利用完我以后\N{\fs16}Once I had served the sorcerer's purpose,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:28.65,正文,,0,0,0,,便把我丢出门外 让我自生自灭\N{\fs16}he threw me out of his house to die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.42,正文,,0,0,0,,可我恨他\N{\fs16}I resolved to live{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.88,正文,,0,0,0,,我偏要活下去\N{\fs16}to spite him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.45,正文,,0,0,0,,我不惜乞讨\N{\fs16}I begged.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.69,正文,,0,0,0,,不惜出卖自己剩下的那部分身体\N{\fs16}I sold what parts of my body remained to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.06,正文,,0,0,0,,直到我变成了一个颇有手段的窃贼\N{\fs16}I became an excellent thief{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.46,正文,,0,0,0,,很快 我发现 一个人信里的东西\N{\fs16}and soon learned that the contents of a man's letters{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:47.56,正文,,0,0,0,,往往比他钱包里的更值钱\N{\fs16}are more valuable than the contents of his purse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.03,正文,,0,0,0,,于是我一步一步忍着\N{\fs16}Step by step,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.83,正文,,0,0,0,,忍着完成一个又一个令人恶心的任务\N{\fs16}one distasteful task after another,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:56.34,正文,,0,0,0,,终于我爬出了密尔的贫民窟\N{\fs16}I made my way from the slums of Myr{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.61,正文,,0,0,0,,坐到了御前议会的桌前\N{\fs16}to the small council chamber.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.48,正文,,0,0,0,,影响力如同野草 火烧不尽 风吹又生\N{\fs16}Influence grows like a weed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.25,正文,,0,0,0,,我以耐心灌溉之\N{\fs16}I tended mine patiently{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.65,正文,,0,0,0,,才使其能绵延繁茂如今 从红堡檐下\N{\fs16}until its tendrils reached from the Red Keep{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:15.02,正文,,0,0,0,,一路不绝 爬到世界的尽头\N{\fs16}all the way across to the far side of the world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:18.99,正文,,0,0,0,,所以我才能够在这野草之下 藏得住那些……\N{\fs16}where I managed to wrap them around something{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.13,正文,,0,0,0,,特别的东西\N{\fs16}very special.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.80,正文,,0,0,0,,那个巫师\N{\fs16}The sorcerer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:32.27,正文,,0,0,0,,你好啊 老朋友\N{\fs16}Hello, my old friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:35.47,正文,,0,0,0,,好久不见啊\N{\fs16}It's been a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.67,正文,,0,0,0,,我坚信 相报有时 而你的仇\N{\fs16}I have no doubt the revenge you want{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.28,正文,,0,0,0,,终将得偿……\N{\fs16}will be yours in time...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:43.34,正文,,0,0,0,,只要你念念不忘 耐心等待\N{\fs16}if you have the stomach for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.75,正文,,0,0,0,,从来没听说过\N{\fs16}When people talk about the Night's Watch,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(218.336,225.958)}{\pos(80,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}葛兰{\b0}\N{\fs12}守夜人游骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.22,正文,,0,0,0,,守夜人还要铲土的……\N{\fs16}they never mention the shoveling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.49,正文,,0,0,0,,还有这些臭屎\N{\fs16}Or the shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.22,正文,,0,0,0,,它们总是拿什么荣誉 赦免来说事儿\N{\fs16}They tell you about honor, pardoning crimes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.66,正文,,0,0,0,,还有保卫王国\N{\fs16}and protecting the realm,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:02.03,正文,,0,0,0,,但其实铲土才是最主要的部分吧\N{\fs16}but shoveling really is most of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:05.76,正文,,0,0,0,,还有遇袭 被杀 甚至更糟\N{\fs16}And getting attacked or killed or worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.26,正文,,0,0,0,,诸如此类 当没有遇袭 被杀的时候\N{\fs16}And that. But when you're not getting attacked or killed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.60,正文,,0,0,0,,基本上都在铲土\N{\fs16}usually you're shoveling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.40,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 快看\N{\fs16}Oh, look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.17,正文,,0,0,0,,更多的屎\N{\fs16}More shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:16.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(266.437,176.161)}{\pos(300,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}艾迪森・托勒特{\b0}\N{\fs12}“忧郁的艾迪” 守夜人事务官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.10,正文,,0,0,0,,我在想今天剩下的时间\N{\fs16}I was starting to wonder what to do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:18.91,正文,,0,0,0,,要做些什么了\N{\fs16}with the rest of my day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.28,正文,,0,0,0,,我们得离开这儿\N{\fs16}We need to get out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.81,正文,,0,0,0,,当司令官大人说走的时候 我们才能走\N{\fs16}When the Lord Commander says we go, we go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.78,正文,,0,0,0,,司令官大人曾让我们去先民拳峰\N{\fs16}The Lord Commander told us to go to the Fist of the First Men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.62,正文,,0,0,0,,- 结果呢？ - 可是他也不知道会变成这样啊\N{\fs16}- How'd that turn out for us? - He had no way of knowing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.12,正文,,0,0,0,,现在我们知道了\N{\fs16}We do now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.85,正文,,0,0,0,,我们知道那有些什么玩意儿了\N{\fs16}We know what's out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.92,正文,,0,0,0,,卡斯特在这儿都能生存下来\N{\fs16}Craster's been out here surviving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:39.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(326.164,279.954)}{\pos(300,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}雷斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}守夜人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.56,正文,,0,0,0,,所以他现在成了你的新任监护人了？\N{\fs16}So he's your new protector now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.09,正文,,0,0,0,,我们的好朋友卡斯特？\N{\fs16}Our good friend Craster?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.83,正文,,0,0,0,,我们就跟他那些丢掉的儿子一样\N{\fs16}We're like the sons he never had.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.43,正文,,0,0,0,,莫尔蒙救不了你\N{\fs16}Mormont isn't gonna save you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.80,正文,,0,0,0,,这些蠢货也救不了你\N{\fs16}This lummox here isn't gonna save you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.17,正文,,0,0,0,,只要异鬼一句话\N{\fs16}When the walkers come calling,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.87,正文,,0,0,0,,卡斯特立刻就会把咱们当猪一样献祭出去\N{\fs16}Craster will serve us up like so many pigs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.24,正文,,0,0,0,,如果我们还想要命……\N{\fs16}If we want to live...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.88,正文,,0,0,0,,我们就得为自己打算\N{\fs16}we'll have to look out for ourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:06.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(424.487,253.857)}{\pos(300,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}吉莉{\b0}\N{\fs12}卡斯特的女儿与妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.18,正文,,0,0,0,,嘘 嘘 嘘\N{\fs16}Shh, shh, shh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:17.86,正文,,0,0,0,,- 你吵醒他了 - 对不起\N{\fs16}- You woke him. - I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.71,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(241.963,251.272)}{\pos(480,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}山姆威尔・塔利{\b0}\N{\fs12}守夜人事务官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.33,正文,,0,0,0,,- 他真美 - 嘘\N{\fs16}- He's beautiful. - Shh!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.90,正文,,0,0,0,,他真美\N{\fs16}He's beautiful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:30.97,正文,,0,0,0,,他有名字么？\N{\fs16}Does he have a name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.60,正文,,0,0,0,,- 没有 - 你要给他起名吗？\N{\fs16}- No. - Are you going to give him one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:36.17,正文,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs16}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.31,正文,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs16}Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:42.80,正文,,0,0,0,,吉莉\N{\fs16}Gilly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.78,正文,,0,0,0,,你说在你回来之前 让我替你保管它\N{\fs16}You said to hold it for you until you came back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.31,正文,,0,0,0,,- 你现在回来了 - 我希望你能留着它\N{\fs16}- You're back. - I wanted you to have it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.31,正文,,0,0,0,,我才不想要这傻乎乎的顶针\N{\fs16}I don't want your stupid thimble.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:51.62,正文,,0,0,0,,我想要救我孩子的命 你能做到吗？\N{\fs16}I want to save my baby's life. Can you do that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.69,正文,,0,0,0,,能吗？\N{\fs16}Can you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.62,正文,,0,0,0,,我没空搭理你\N{\fs16}I don't have time for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.96,正文,,0,0,0,,除了他 我没空搭理任何人\N{\fs16}I don't have time for anyone but him{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.19,正文,,0,0,0,,因为他没多少时间了\N{\fs16}because he doesn't have much time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.62,正文,,0,0,0,,你得去找他\N{\fs16}You have to go after him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.52,正文,,0,0,0,,怎么找？\N{\fs16}How?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:36.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(439.42,275.973)}{\pos(200,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}布兰・史塔克{\b0}\N{\fs12}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:34.62,正文,,0,0,0,,你知道该怎么找\N{\fs16}You know how.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.44,正文,,0,0,0,,布兰登\N{\fs16}Brandon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.15,正文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs16}Mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.63,正文,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过多少次了\N{\fs16}How many times have I told you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.32,正文,,0,0,0,,- 不要攀爬 - 妈妈 我得找到它\N{\fs16}- No climbing. - Mother, I need to find it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:08.08,正文,,0,0,0,,- 它就在这儿 它在召唤我 - 你得向我保证\N{\fs16}- It's here. It's calling me. - I want you to promise me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.41,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(166.731,281.635)}{\pos(250,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}凯特琳・徒利{\b0}\N{\fs12}艾德・史塔克的遗孀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.05,正文,,0,0,0,,别再爬了 答应我\N{\fs16}No more climbing. Promise me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.75,正文,,0,0,0,,答应我！ 答应我！\N{\fs16}Promise me! Promise me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.09,正文,,0,0,0,,-妈妈！妈妈！ -答应我！答应我 布兰！\N{\fs16}- Mother! Mother! - Promise me! Promise me, Bran!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.36,正文,,0,0,0,,答应我！\N{\fs16}Promise me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:25.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(379.975,258.759)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}玖健・黎德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.70,正文,,0,0,0,,他那活儿很大？\N{\fs16}Is he very large?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.51,正文,,0,0,0,,看起来也没大多少\N{\fs16}No larger than usual, apparently.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:35.57,正文,,0,0,0,,- 不过她们说他…… - 不同寻常\N{\fs16}- And yet they said that he was-- - Extraordinary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.21,正文,,0,0,0,,她们所见过的最特别的男人\N{\fs16}The most extraordinary man they've ever had.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:39.41,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(456.338,273.195)}{\pos(50,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}萝丝{\b0}\N{\fs12}妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.68,正文,,0,0,0,,她们可是阅人无数\N{\fs16}And they've had a lot of men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.71,正文,,0,0,0,,我们说的是同一个波德瑞克吗？\N{\fs16}We're talking about the same Podrick?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.28,正文,,0,0,0,,给提利昂大人当侍从的那个闷小子？\N{\fs16}The quiet boy in Lord Tyrion's service?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.88,正文,,0,0,0,,看上去很天真的那个？\N{\fs16}Seems a bit simple?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.92,正文,,0,0,0,,他对她们做了什么？\N{\fs16}What did he do to them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.22,正文,,0,0,0,,这我可不知道 大人\N{\fs16}I don't know, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.62,正文,,0,0,0,,这群姑娘们通常很会夸夸其谈的不是么\N{\fs16}The girls are usually quite descriptive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.59,正文,,0,0,0,,她们怎么说的？\N{\fs16}So what did they say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.66,正文,,0,0,0,,她们说这回不太好解释\N{\fs16}They said it was hard to describe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.26,正文,,0,0,0,,这\N{\fs16}Huh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:04.03,正文,,0,0,0,,人才出现在了最古怪的地方\N{\fs16}Prodigies appear in the oddest of places.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:08.27,正文,,0,0,0,,那小指头呢？对他的损失有什么反应？\N{\fs16}And what did Littlefinger say about this loss of income?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.37,正文,,0,0,0,,他太忙了 才没空管这些\N{\fs16}He was too preoccupied to notice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.71,正文,,0,0,0,,他即将动身去鹰巢城了\N{\fs16}He's leaving for the Eyrie soon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.24,正文,,0,0,0,,我在帮他打点行装\N{\fs16}I'm helping him prepare for his journey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.88,正文,,0,0,0,,啊是啊 去追求他与艾林夫人不朽的爱情\N{\fs16}Ah, yes, to pursue his enduring love{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.41,正文,,0,0,0,,还有那随她而来的名号\N{\fs16}of the Lady Arryn and the title that comes with her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.55,正文,,0,0,0,,真是可悲\N{\fs16}Sad, really.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.55,正文,,0,0,0,,这就让我们的朋友\N{\fs16}Is that all it takes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.68,正文,,0,0,0,,对可怜的珊莎・史塔克失去兴趣了么？\N{\fs16}to make our friend lose interest in poor Sansa Stark?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.25,正文,,0,0,0,,自从上次之后他就没和她再交谈过了\N{\fs16}He hasn't spoken to her since the last time,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.09,正文,,0,0,0,,至少据我所知如此\N{\fs16}as far as I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.76,正文,,0,0,0,,我倒不认为他失去兴趣了\N{\fs16}But I don't think he's lost interest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.89,正文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fs16}What makes you say so?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.30,正文,,0,0,0,,- 他的登船清单 - 噢\N{\fs16}- His shipboard inventory. - Ah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.60,正文,,0,0,0,,你认字\N{\fs16}You can read.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.70,正文,,0,0,0,,干咱们这行的姑娘中这还真少见\N{\fs16}Rare for a woman in your profession.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:50.74,正文,,0,0,0,,- 老本行 - 当然\N{\fs16}- Former profession. - Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:54.34,正文,,0,0,0,,对了我们还是回归正题吧 你刚才想说什么来着？\N{\fs16}I'm missing something obvious you're about to point out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.27,正文,,0,0,0,,两张羽毛床\N{\fs16}Two featherbeds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.84,正文,,0,0,0,,他要把两张羽毛床搬到床上\N{\fs16}He's bringing two featherbeds for the cabin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.18,正文,,0,0,0,,除了小指头自己 还能有谁这么重要\N{\fs16}Who is important enough to Littlefinger{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:06.02,正文,,0,0,0,,得劳驾小指头带上羽毛床？\N{\fs16}to merit a featherbed besides Littlefinger?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.29,正文,,0,0,0,,可能他带着他的一个姑娘？\N{\fs16}Could he be bringing one of his girls?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.62,正文,,0,0,0,,他对她们可没兴趣 大人\N{\fs16}He's not interested in them, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.39,正文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？\N{\fs16}How do you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.83,正文,,0,0,0,,因为我就是她们中的一个\N{\fs16}Because I'm one of his girls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:18.29,正文,,0,0,0,,真是怪处出人才\N{\fs16}Prodigies in odd places indeed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.83,正文,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉・坦格利安是被她弟弟所谋害的\N{\fs16}Rhaenyra Targaryen was murdered by her brother,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.33,正文,,0,0,0,,或者说是她弟弟的龙\N{\fs16}or rather his dragon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.97,正文,,0,0,0,,这野兽在她儿子面前吃了她\N{\fs16}It ate her while her son watched.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.84,正文,,0,0,0,,这下面地穴里埋着的 是她被吃剩的残尸\N{\fs16}What's left of her is buried in the crypts right down there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.95,正文,,0,0,0,,遵照传统婚礼将会在大圣堂里举行\N{\fs16}The ceremony is traditionally held in the main sanctum,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:42.22,正文,,0,0,0,,那里摆得下700个座位\N{\fs16}which seats 700 comfortably.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.92,正文,,0,0,0,,看起来应该在厅里再安排些席位\N{\fs16}There appears to be a good deal of room elsewhere{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.55,正文,,0,0,0,,以接纳其它的来客\N{\fs16}on the premises for everyone else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:50.76,正文,,0,0,0,,可我们要宴请的贵宾只有700个啊\N{\fs16}There aren't more than 700 people of any importance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.93,正文,,0,0,0,,的确 剩下的都是来捧人场的\N{\fs16}No, the rest are there to look adoringly{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.99,正文,,0,0,0,,让那700个人意识到自己\N{\fs16}upon the 700 to remind them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.20,正文,,0,0,0,,是有多么的荣幸才能位列贵席\N{\fs16}how superior they must be to have the best seats.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.73,正文,,0,0,0,,在那个瓮里的是\N{\fs16}Over there in that urn,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.61,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(166.457,225.064)}{\pos(320,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}瑟曦・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}摄政太后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.61,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(378.084,221.189)}{\pos(140,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}奥莲娜夫人{\b0}\N{\fs12}玛格丽・提利尔的祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:03.10,正文,,0,0,0,,伊里昂・坦格利安的骨灰\N{\fs16}the ashes of Aerion Targaryen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.10,正文,,0,0,0,,人称“明焰”伊里昂\N{\fs16}Aerion Brightflame they called him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:08.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(530.36,264.247)}{\pos(140,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}玛格丽・提利尔{\b0}\N{\fs12}乔佛里国王的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:08.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(360.986,263.184)}{\pos(420,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}乔佛里・拜拉席恩{\b0}\N{\fs12}铁王座上的王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:08.31,正文,,0,0,0,,他相信喝下野火就能变成真龙\N{\fs16}He thought drinking wildfire would turn him into a dragon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.54,正文,,0,0,0,,显然他错了\N{\fs16}He was wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.61,正文,,0,0,0,,当然 那儿还有疯王\N{\fs16}And, of course, there's the Mad King,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.38,正文,,0,0,0,,我舅舅杀死的那个\N{\fs16}killed by my uncle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:18.61,正文,,0,0,0,,你想看看最后的坦格利安被埋在哪里吗？\N{\fs16}Would you like to see where the last Targaryens are buried?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.62,正文,,0,0,0,,你确定玛格丽小姐不会觉得这有点恐怖吗？\N{\fs16}Are you sure Lady Margaery doesn't find all this a bit macabre?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.39,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 不会 没有什么的 陛下\N{\fs16}Oh, no, it's quite all right, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.99,正文,,0,0,0,,我很想看看他们的墓穴\N{\fs16}I'd love to see their tombs, really.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.32,正文,,0,0,0,,就像是在历史中漫步一样\N{\fs16}It's like taking a walk through history.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.60,正文,,0,0,0,,- 墓穴就在那里 C真是让人激动\N{\fs16}- The tomb's just up here. - This is so exciting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:36.27,正文,,0,0,0,,您是在这里成婚的么 陛下？\N{\fs16}You were married here, Your Grace?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.47,正文,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 一定就像是昨天一样\N{\fs16}- Yes. - Must seem like only yesterday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.27,正文,,0,0,0,,就像是上辈子的事情\N{\fs16}Seems like a lifetime ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.64,正文,,0,0,0,,您的亡夫 也埋葬在这里吗？\N{\fs16}Your husband, was he buried here as well?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.77,正文,,0,0,0,,不 他希望将遗骨葬在风息堡\N{\fs16}No, he wanted his remains returned to Storm's End.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:50.37,正文,,0,0,0,,- 真是个悲剧 - 一个显而易见的悲剧\N{\fs16}- Such a tragedy. - A fairly predictable tragedy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.94,正文,,0,0,0,,打猎的时候怎么能够酗酒\N{\fs16}Hunting and drinking don't mix.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.54,正文,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\N{\fs16}I should say not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.65,正文,,0,0,0,,我儿子是个猎人 这总是让他忘记\N{\fs16}My son's a hunter. It helps him forget{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.55,正文,,0,0,0,,自己从未接近过真刀真枪的战争\N{\fs16}he's never been within a mile of a real battle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.55,正文,,0,0,0,,可我记得他曾经围攻过风息堡\N{\fs16}I seem to recall he laid siege to Storm's End{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.12,正文,,0,0,0,,围城了大半年了\N{\fs16}for the better part of a year.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.89,正文,,0,0,0,,他围攻的\N{\fs16}All he laid siege to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.22,正文,,0,0,0,,不过是他大帐里的宴席而已\N{\fs16}was the banquet table in the command tent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:10.49,正文,,0,0,0,,我警告过他别参与劳勃的叛乱\N{\fs16}I told him to stay out of Robert's rebellion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:14.03,正文,,0,0,0,,他根本没那个实力 去和真正的战士较量\N{\fs16}He had no business fighting an actual warrior.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:17.50,正文,,0,0,0,,我们这些母亲总是极尽所能地\N{\fs16}We mothers do what we can{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.70,正文,,0,0,0,,让自己的儿子远离死亡\N{\fs16}to keep our sons from the grave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.74,正文,,0,0,0,,不过他们却为之乐此不疲\N{\fs16}But they do seem to yearn for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:24.50,正文,,0,0,0,,我们灌输给他们的理智\N{\fs16}We shower them with good sense,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.04,正文,,0,0,0,,像羽翼上的雨滴一样潸然流走\N{\fs16}and it slides right off like rain off a wing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.04,正文,,0,0,0,,可现实是 这世道是属于他们的\N{\fs16}And yet the world belongs to them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.98,正文,,0,0,0,,真是个荒唐的安排啊\N{\fs16}A ridiculous arrangement, to my mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.88,正文,,0,0,0,,也许七神认为这是合适的安排吧\N{\fs16}The gods have seen fit to make it so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.59,正文,,0,0,0,,我父亲不希望他们留在这里\N{\fs16}My father didn't want them here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.25,正文,,0,0,0,,他要烧了他们的遗体\N{\fs16}He was going to have their bodies burned{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.95,正文,,0,0,0,,然后丢进黑水河去\N{\fs16}and thrown in the Blackwater,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:50.49,正文,,0,0,0,,不过大主教让他改了主意\N{\fs16}but the High Septon convinced him otherwise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.16,正文,,0,0,0,,我很高兴他这么做了\N{\fs16}I'm glad he did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.56,正文,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 陛下\N{\fs16}I'm sorry, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.33,正文,,0,0,0,,我明白他们最后做了很糟糕的事\N{\fs16}I know they did terrible things at the end,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:01.27,正文,,0,0,0,,但是他们的祖先建造了这个城堡\N{\fs16}but their ancestors built this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.10,正文,,0,0,0,,有的时候疯狂\N{\fs16}Sometimes severity{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.27,正文,,0,0,0,,是换取伟大的代价\N{\fs16}is the price we pay for greatness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:11.61,正文,,0,0,0,,感同身受\N{\fs16}I couldn't agree more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.65,正文,,0,0,0,,我们要去看他们吗？\N{\fs16}Shall we go and see them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:26.12,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你给予他们爱\N{\fs16}If you give them your love,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:29.59,正文,,0,0,0,,他们会千万倍的奉还\N{\fs16}they will return it a thousandfold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:32.13,正文,,0,0,0,,我和他们交谈过\N{\fs16}I've spoken with them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.50,正文,,0,0,0,,我知道他们怎么看待你\N{\fs16}I know how they feel about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.97,正文,,0,0,0,,你领导了君临的防御战\N{\fs16}You led the defense of King's Landing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.70,正文,,0,0,0,,他们崇拜你\N{\fs16}They adore you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.25,正文,,0,0,0,,把门打开\N{\fs16}Open the doors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.59,正文,,0,0,0,,乔佛里\N{\fs16}Joffrey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.42,正文,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs16}Wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:07.36,正文,,0,0,0,,- 玛格丽小姐！ - 玛格丽小姐！\N{\fs16}- Lady Margaery! - Lady Margaery!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:10.16,正文,,0,0,0,,祝福你 玛格丽小姐！\N{\fs16}Bless you, Lady Margaery!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.63,正文,,0,0,0,,- 玛格丽小姐！ - 玛格丽小姐！\N{\fs16}- Lady Margaery! - Lady Margaery!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.70,正文,,0,0,0,,- 玛格丽！ - 玛格丽小姐万岁！\N{\fs16}- Margaery! - Long live Lady Margaery!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:18.23,正文,,0,0,0,,乔佛里国王！\N{\fs16}King Joffrey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.51,正文,,0,0,0,,乔佛里国王！乔佛里国王！\N{\fs16}King Joffrey! King Joffrey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.64,正文,,0,0,0,,乔佛里国王！\N{\fs16}King Joffrey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.94,正文,,0,0,0,,七神祝福乔佛里国王！\N{\fs16}Gods bless King Joffrey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.68,正文,,0,0,0,,离深林堡还有多远？\N{\fs16}How far is it to Deepwood Motte?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.28,正文,,0,0,0,,不远了 大人\N{\fs16}Not far, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.28,正文,,0,0,0,,你的姐姐在那等你\N{\fs16}Your sister is waiting for you there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.12,正文,,0,0,0,,- 她派你来救我的？ - 没错\N{\fs16}- She sent you to save me? - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:44.99,正文,,0,0,0,,我曾为那些折磨你的人效命\N{\fs16}I served them, the men who were torturing you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.59,正文,,0,0,0,,我照他们说的去做 直到时机成熟\N{\fs16}I did what they told me and waited for the right moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.99,正文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要为我冒险？\N{\fs16}Why would you risk your life for me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:50.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(229.216,232.295)}{\pos(250,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}席恩・葛雷乔伊{\b0}\N{\fs12}铁群岛继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:53.03,正文,,0,0,0,,我是在盐崖岛长大的 大人\N{\fs16}I grew up on Saltcliffe, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:56.20,正文,,0,0,0,,他们把你带走的时候我还是个小孩\N{\fs16}I was only a boy when they took you away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.20,正文,,0,0,0,,我的父亲把我和我的兄弟们带到断崖上\N{\fs16}My father brought me and my brothers up to the bluffs{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.24,正文,,0,0,0,,我们目送载着你的船离去\N{\fs16}so we could watch the ship that carried you off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.31,正文,,0,0,0,,我还记得我父亲的神情 当他说\N{\fs16}I remember the look on my father's face when he told us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.14,正文,,0,0,0,,“这是巴隆・葛雷乔伊唯一活着的儿子”\N{\fs16}"That's Balon Greyjoy's last living son."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.88,正文,,0,0,0,,当我看到他们折磨你的时候\N{\fs16}And those are the words I heard over and over again{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:13.21,正文,,0,0,0,,这些话就在我的脑中回响个不停\N{\fs16}when I saw what they were doing to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.25,正文,,0,0,0,,那些人\N{\fs16}Those men,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.28,正文,,0,0,0,,他们说我父亲知道他们对我做什么\N{\fs16}they said my father knew what they were doing to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:22.19,正文,,0,0,0,,是真的吗？\N{\fs16}Did he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.16,正文,,0,0,0,,我…… 我不知道 大人\N{\fs16}I-- I don't know, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:28.66,正文,,0,0,0,,他们…… 他们从来不会告诉我很多\N{\fs16}They-- they never told me much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.27,正文,,0,0,0,,我姐姐的人都很忠诚\N{\fs16}My sister's men are loyal to her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.47,正文,,0,0,0,,我不需要躲躲藏藏的\N{\fs16}We don't need to hide from them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.54,正文,,0,0,0,,可并不是所有的人都是你姐姐的部下\N{\fs16}Not all those are your sister's men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.28,正文,,0,0,0,,还有些人是忠于你父亲的\N{\fs16}Some of them are loyal to your father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.61,正文,,0,0,0,,这是做什么？\N{\fs16}What is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.25,正文,,0,0,0,,只是在想那时我是如何被妒火吞没的\N{\fs16}I was just thinking how jealous I was{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.42,正文,,0,0,0,,当我听到父亲命令雅拉攻打这里的时候\N{\fs16}when my father told Yara to take this place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.22,正文,,0,0,0,,他给你安排了什么任务？\N{\fs16}What did he tell you to do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.45,正文,,0,0,0,,去掠夺渔村\N{\fs16}Raid fishing villages.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.32,正文,,0,0,0,,他不信任我\N{\fs16}He didn't trust me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.12,正文,,0,0,0,,他认为我是个史塔克\N{\fs16}Thought I was a Stark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:06.09,正文,,0,0,0,,呵呵 我永远都不会成为史塔克\N{\fs16}Ha. I could never be a Stark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:08.59,正文,,0,0,0,,罗柏・史塔克总是提醒我这点\N{\fs16}Robb Stark always reminded me of that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:11.13,正文,,0,0,0,,- 他曾经凌驾于你之上么？ - 他没这个必要\N{\fs16}- He lorded it over you? - Didn't have to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:14.33,正文,,0,0,0,,他只需顺其自然就够了\N{\fs16}All he had to do was be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.37,正文,,0,0,0,,他生来就高人一等\N{\fs16}Be who he was born to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.87,正文,,0,0,0,,他的人生是如此的一帆风顺\N{\fs16}His life fit him better than his clothes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:23.41,正文,,0,0,0,,像他这样的人 又怎么会拿我当兄弟呢？\N{\fs16}How could someone like that ever be a brother to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.71,正文,,0,0,0,,他可是北境之王\N{\fs16}He's the King in the North.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.04,正文,,0,0,0,,而我……\N{\fs16}And me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.75,正文,,0,0,0,,我父亲给了我一个选择\N{\fs16}my father gave me a choice{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.68,正文,,0,0,0,,我也做出了决定\N{\fs16}and I made it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.02,正文,,0,0,0,,我不可能成为一个史塔克\N{\fs16}I could never be a Stark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:38.52,正文,,0,0,0,,我是个铁种\N{\fs16}But ironborn,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.19,正文,,0,0,0,,这才是我生来的命运\N{\fs16}that's what I was born to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.63,正文,,0,0,0,,我付铁钱换来了临冬城\N{\fs16}I paid the iron price for Winterfell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.24,正文,,0,0,0,,我谋杀了那两个男孩\N{\fs16}I murdered those boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:02.14,正文,,0,0,0,,史塔克家的男孩？\N{\fs16}The Stark boys?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.25,正文,,0,0,0,,我就没找到过他们\N{\fs16}Never found them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.92,正文,,0,0,0,,我杀的不过是农夫家养的可怜孤儿\N{\fs16}Just some poor orphans living with a farmer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:15.12,正文,,0,0,0,,我让达格摩割了他们的喉咙\N{\fs16}I let Dagmer slit their throats{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.32,正文,,0,0,0,,然后让他们烧掉尸体\N{\fs16}and I let him burn the bodies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.76,正文,,0,0,0,,这样我就能占有临冬城\N{\fs16}so I could keep Winterfell...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:26.30,正文,,0,0,0,,让我父亲骄傲\N{\fs16}and make my father proud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.80,正文,,0,0,0,,也许还不算太晚\N{\fs16}Maybe it's not too late.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:34.97,正文,,0,0,0,,已经太晚了\N{\fs16}It is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:46.01,正文,,0,0,0,,我真正的父亲在君临掉了脑袋\N{\fs16}My real father lost his head at King's Landing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.09,正文,,0,0,0,,而我 已经做过了选择……\N{\fs16}I made a choice...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:54.66,正文,,0,0,0,,一个错误的选择\N{\fs16}and I chose wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:59.83,正文,,0,0,0,,现在我把一切都搞砸了\N{\fs16}And now I've burned everything down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:03.86,正文,,0,0,0,,不是一切 大人\N{\fs16}Not everything, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:08.00,正文,,0,0,0,,她来了\N{\fs16}She's up here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.91,正文,,0,0,0,,- 雅拉 - 嘘\N{\fs16}- Yara. - Shh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:24.48,正文,,0,0,0,,等着\N{\fs16}Wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.59,正文,,0,0,0,,我带他回来了 他杀了其他人\N{\fs16}I brought him back. He killed the others.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:37.46,正文,,0,0,0,,什么？我没有\N{\fs16}What? No, I didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:39.66,正文,,0,0,0,,你不能！\N{\fs16}You can't!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:42.40,正文,,0,0,0,,不 停下！\N{\fs16}No, please stop!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:47.73,正文,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs16}No!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:49.53,正文,,0,0,0,,把他扔回属于他的地方去\N{\fs16}Put him back where he belongs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:15.49,正文,,0,0,0,,吃吧\N{\fs16}Eat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:21.03,正文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\N{\fs16}What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.66,正文,,0,0,0,,我要死了\N{\fs16}I'm dying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:26.67,正文,,0,0,0,,你不能\N{\fs16}You can't die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.00,正文,,0,0,0,,你得活下去\N{\fs16}You need to live{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:31.50,正文,,0,0,0,,活下去复仇\N{\fs16}to take revenge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:34.01,正文,,0,0,0,,我才不管什么复仇了\N{\fs16}I don't care about revenge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:36.01,正文,,0,0,0,,你个懦夫\N{\fs16}You coward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:39.94,正文,,0,0,0,,不过是这么一点不如意 你就放弃了\N{\fs16}A little misfortune and you're giving up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:43.55,正文,,0,0,0,,不如……\N{\fs16}mis-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:45.15,正文,,0,0,0,,不如意？\N{\fs16}misfortune?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:46.95,正文,,0,0,0,,我失去了我的手\N{\fs16}You lost your hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:49.72,正文,,0,0,0,,那是我用剑的手 我就是那只手\N{\fs16}My sword hand. I was that hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:54.29,正文,,0,0,0,,你终于尝到了――\N{\fs16}You have a taste--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:57.02,正文,,0,0,0,,真实世界的滋味\N{\fs16}one taste of the real world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:24:00.16,正文,,0,0,0,,一旦被夺走了重要的事物\N{\fs16}where people have important things taken from them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:02.96,正文,,0,0,0,,就哭天喊地 心灰意冷\N{\fs16}and you whine and cry and quit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.47,正文,,0,0,0,,你听起来像个娘们\N{\fs16}You sound like a bloody woman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:33.49,正文,,0,0,0,,我知道你为我做了什么\N{\fs16}I know what you did for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.76,0:24:37.76,正文,,0,0,0,,你跟他们说塔斯全是蓝宝石\N{\fs16}You told them Tarth was full of sapphires.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.76,0:24:43.73,正文,,0,0,0,,塔斯之所以被称为蓝宝石岛\N{\fs16}It's called the Sapphire Isle{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.77,0:24:45.93,正文,,0,0,0,,是因为那里蔚蓝的海水\N{\fs16}because of the blue of its water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.87,0:24:51.04,正文,,0,0,0,,你是知道的\N{\fs16}You knew that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.18,0:25:00.51,正文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要帮我？\N{\fs16}Why did you help me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:28.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(545.184,246.416)}{\pos(380,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}泰温・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}凯岩城公爵 国王之手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.57,0:25:28.30,正文,,0,0,0,,你找我？\N{\fs16}You wanted to speak to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.34,0:25:30.70,正文,,0,0,0,,对 关于詹姆\N{\fs16}Yes, about Jaime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.77,0:25:33.37,正文,,0,0,0,,他怎么了？\N{\fs16}What about him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.41,0:25:34.81,正文,,0,0,0,,我想确保\N{\fs16}I wanted to make sure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.84,0:25:37.28,正文,,0,0,0,,我们会尽全力让他回来\N{\fs16}we're doing everything we can to get him back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.61,0:25:43.48,正文,,0,0,0,,凯特琳・史塔克当初抓走提利昂……\N{\fs16}When Catelyn Stark took Tyrion prisoner...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.08,0:25:46.82,正文,,0,0,0,,我是怎么回应的？\N{\fs16}what did I do in response?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.85,0:25:49.89,正文,,0,0,0,,- 您发动了一场战争  - 既然我会\N{\fs16}- You started a war. - And if I would start a war{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.92,0:25:52.29,正文,,0,0,0,,为了那个好色的小残废发动一场战争\N{\fs16}for that lecherous little stump,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.32,0:25:55.49,正文,,0,0,0,,为了我的长子和继承人 你说我会怎么做？\N{\fs16}what do you think I am doing for my oldest son and heir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.53,0:25:58.19,正文,,0,0,0,,尽您所能\N{\fs16}Whatever you can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.23,0:26:01.00,正文,,0,0,0,,尽我所能\N{\fs16}Whatever I can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.84,0:26:15.11,正文,,0,0,0,,- 还不走啊 - 对\N{\fs16}- You're still here. - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.85,0:26:20.28,正文,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs16}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.31,0:26:21.71,正文,,0,0,0,,您有没有想过\N{\fs16}Did it ever occur to you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.75,0:26:23.75,正文,,0,0,0,,也许我是最值得您信任的人\N{\fs16}that I might be the one who deserves your confidence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.78,0:26:26.25,正文,,0,0,0,,而不是您的儿子们？\N{\fs16}and your trust, not your sons?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.29,0:26:29.15,正文,,0,0,0,,不是詹姆也不是提利昂 是我\N{\fs16}Not Jaime or Tyrion, but me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.19,0:26:31.39,正文,,0,0,0,,年复一年的教诲\N{\fs16}Years and years of lectures on family{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.42,0:26:33.49,正文,,0,0,0,,有关家族和祖传家业\N{\fs16}and legacy--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.53,0:26:35.03,正文,,0,0,0,,千篇一律\N{\fs16}the same lecture, really,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.06,0:26:38.36,正文,,0,0,0,,只有乏味而微小的改变\N{\fs16}just with tiny, tedious variations--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.40,0:26:40.13,正文,,0,0,0,,不知您是否意识到您的女儿\N{\fs16}did it ever occur to you that your daughter{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.16,0:26:41.89,正文,,0,0,0,,可能是唯一把教诲听进去的人？\N{\fs16}might be the only one listening to them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.92,0:26:43.45,正文,,0,0,0,,可能是唯一以此为信念的人\N{\fs16}Living by them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.87,0:26:47.44,正文,,0,0,0,,您把祖训看得比自己的孩子们要重要得多\N{\fs16}That she might have the most to contribute to your legacy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.47,0:26:50.37,正文,,0,0,0,,而她也许最能帮助您去完成\N{\fs16}that you love so much more than your actual children?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.41,0:27:00.51,正文,,0,0,0,,好吧 来帮助我\N{\fs16}All right. Contribute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.88,0:27:05.29,正文,,0,0,0,,提利尔家族是个问题\N{\fs16}The Tyrells are a problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.62,0:27:09.89,正文,,0,0,0,,提利尔家族帮我们打败了史坦尼斯・拜拉席恩\N{\fs16}The Tyrells helped us defeat Stannis Baratheon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.92,0:27:13.19,正文,,0,0,0,,提利尔家族救了你的命 救了你孩子们的命\N{\fs16}The Tyrells saved your life, your children's lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.59,0:27:16.93,正文,,0,0,0,,玛格丽将魔爪伸向了乔佛里\N{\fs16}Margaery has her claws in Joffrey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.73,0:27:20.93,正文,,0,0,0,,她懂得如何操控他\N{\fs16}She knows how to manipulate him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.97,0:27:22.33,正文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs16}Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.37,0:27:24.47,正文,,0,0,0,,我真希望你也懂得如何操控他\N{\fs16}I wish you knew how to manipulate him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.87,0:27:28.44,正文,,0,0,0,,我不信任你 不是因为你是女人\N{\fs16}I don't distrust you because you're a woman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.47,0:27:31.98,正文,,0,0,0,,而是因为你自以为是\N{\fs16}I distrust you because you're not as smart as you think you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.01,0:27:34.78,正文,,0,0,0,,你让儿子骑在你头上\N{\fs16}You've allowed that boy to ride roughshod over you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.81,0:27:37.78,正文,,0,0,0,,还任凭他欺压城里的所有人\N{\fs16}and everyone else in this city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.79,0:27:45.16,正文,,0,0,0,,也许......\N{\fs16}Perhaps...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.19,0:27:48.66,正文,,0,0,0,,您应该阻止他为所欲为\N{\fs16}you should try stopping him from doing what he likes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.00,0:27:55.13,正文,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\fs16}I will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.47,0:27:58.37,正文,,0,0,0,,您喜欢吗 奶奶？\N{\fs16}Do you like it, Nana?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:28:01.27,正文,,0,0,0,,又一朵金玫瑰 真没劲\N{\fs16}Another golden rose. How original.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.30,0:28:03.71,正文,,0,0,0,,我吃饭的盘子里刻着玫瑰\N{\fs16}I eat from plates stamped with roses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.74,0:28:05.94,正文,,0,0,0,,我睡觉的被单上绣着玫瑰\N{\fs16}I sleep in sheets embroidered with roses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:08.84,正文,,0,0,0,,我的夜壶上画着金玫瑰\N{\fs16}I have a golden rose painted on my chamber pot,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.88,0:28:11.28,正文,,0,0,0,,难道这样就能好闻点\N{\fs16}as if that makes it smell any better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.31,0:28:12.98,正文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 玫瑰很无趣\N{\fs16}Roses are boring, dear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.01,0:28:15.55,正文,,0,0,0,,“生生不息”\N{\fs16}"Growing strong."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.58,0:28:18.68,正文,,0,0,0,,所有家族中最无趣的族语\N{\fs16}Ha! The dullest words of any house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.72,0:28:20.62,正文,,0,0,0,,“凛冬将至！”\N{\fs16}"Winter is coming!"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.65,0:28:22.69,正文,,0,0,0,,这才让人过目不忘\N{\fs16}Now that's memorable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.72,0:28:25.79,正文,,0,0,0,,“强取胜于苦耕”多么强大\N{\fs16}"We do not sow." Strong. Strong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.83,0:28:27.86,正文,,0,0,0,,这些才是你会防备的家族\N{\fs16}Those are houses you watch out for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.89,0:28:32.03,正文,,0,0,0,,冰原狼 海怪 凶猛的野兽\N{\fs16}Direwolves and krakens, fierce beasts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.06,0:28:34.06,正文,,0,0,0,,但生生不息的金玫瑰――\N{\fs16}But a golden rose growing strong--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:37.47,正文,,0,0,0,,哈 真让人心惊胆战\N{\fs16}ha, that strikes fear in the heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.70,0:28:41.94,正文,,0,0,0,,瞧 小可爱们\N{\fs16}Look, little loves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.97,0:28:43.87,正文,,0,0,0,,花园里来了只蜘蛛\N{\fs16}A spider in the garden.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.01,0:28:46.71,正文,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs16}Run along now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.74,0:28:48.68,正文,,0,0,0,,生生不息\N{\fs16}Grow strong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.71,0:28:52.25,正文,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fs16}My lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.28,0:28:55.62,正文,,0,0,0,,我想亲自欢迎您来到君临\N{\fs16}I wanted to personally welcome you to King's Landing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.65,0:28:58.12,正文,,0,0,0,,城市因您的到来而熠熠生辉\N{\fs16}The city has been made brighter by your presence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.15,0:29:01.22,正文,,0,0,0,,城市因我的到来而熠熠生辉？\N{\fs16}The city is made brighter by my presence?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.26,0:29:03.62,正文,,0,0,0,,这是你的常用台词吗 瓦里斯大人？\N{\fs16}Is that your usual line, Lord Varys?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.66,0:29:05.22,正文,,0,0,0,,你是来找我搭讪的吗？\N{\fs16}Are you here to seduce me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.26,0:29:06.93,正文,,0,0,0,,也许是有点明显了\N{\fs16}A little obvious, perhaps.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.96,0:29:08.86,正文,,0,0,0,,哦不 请便\N{\fs16}Oh, no, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.90,0:29:12.26,正文,,0,0,0,,都这么久了 请继续吧\N{\fs16}Seduce away. It's been so long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.30,0:29:14.67,正文,,0,0,0,,但我觉得你这是白费力气\N{\fs16}Though I rather think it's all for naught.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.70,0:29:18.34,正文,,0,0,0,,一个缺东西的和一个老太婆能发生什么？\N{\fs16}What happens when the nonexistent bumps against the decrepit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.54,0:29:21.64,正文,,0,0,0,,这个问题留给哲学家吧\N{\fs16}A question for the philosophers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.67,0:29:24.71,正文,,0,0,0,,可你绕了这么久的弯子 究竟为了什么而来？\N{\fs16}But you've come mincing all this way for something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.74,0:29:26.88,正文,,0,0,0,,- 说吧？ - 我能坐下吗？\N{\fs16}- So? - Might I sit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.91,0:29:28.81,正文,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs16}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.85,0:29:32.01,正文,,0,0,0,,说吧 我听说你是个聪明人\N{\fs16}Come, I've heard you're such a clever man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.05,0:29:34.75,正文,,0,0,0,,我很好奇你为什么来找我\N{\fs16}I'm curious why you've sought me out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.95,0:29:38.52,正文,,0,0,0,,您对珊莎・史塔克很有兴趣\N{\fs16}You've taken an interest in Sansa Stark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.55,0:29:39.69,正文,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fs16}Have I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.72,0:29:41.59,正文,,0,0,0,,就因为我和她在这花园里聊过一次\N{\fs16}Because I spoke to her once in this garden{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:44.52,正文,,0,0,0,,你的探子就跑去报告了？\N{\fs16}and one of your little spies came running to tell you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.56,0:29:45.86,正文,,0,0,0,,我为什么不能感兴趣？\N{\fs16}Why shouldn't I take an interest?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.89,0:29:47.66,正文,,0,0,0,,- 她是个引人注意的女孩 - 是吗？\N{\fs16}- She's an interesting girl. - Is she?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.70,0:29:49.50,正文,,0,0,0,,不 并没什么特别之处\N{\fs16}No, not particularly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.53,0:29:51.56,正文,,0,0,0,,不过她的童年倒是让人颇感兴趣\N{\fs16}But she's had an interesting childhood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.60,0:29:54.37,正文,,0,0,0,,是啊 悲惨的童年\N{\fs16}She has, sadly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.40,0:29:56.70,正文,,0,0,0,,请原谅 浪费了您的时间\N{\fs16}Well, forgive me for wasting your time, then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.74,0:30:00.07,正文,,0,0,0,,我原以为我们都对她的幸福心怀关切\N{\fs16}I thought we shared certain hopes for her well-being.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.11,0:30:01.57,正文,,0,0,0,,得了吧\N{\fs16}Come, come.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.61,0:30:04.17,正文,,0,0,0,,你不能这么快就缴械投降了\N{\fs16}You surrender rather easily.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.68,0:30:07.04,正文,,0,0,0,,和我走一走\N{\fs16}Walk with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.08,0:30:08.81,正文,,0,0,0,,我知道隔墙有耳\N{\fs16}I know the walls have ears,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.85,0:30:11.18,正文,,0,0,0,,但很显然 灌木丛中也有\N{\fs16}but apparently the shrubbery does, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.21,0:30:14.02,正文,,0,0,0,,我挑选同盟很小心\N{\fs16}I choose my allies carefully{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.05,0:30:17.02,正文,,0,0,0,,挑选敌人则会更加小心\N{\fs16}and my enemies more carefully still.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.05,0:30:18.95,正文,,0,0,0,,珊莎是同盟还是敌人？\N{\fs16}Which is Sansa Stark?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.99,0:30:21.79,正文,,0,0,0,,都不是 涉世未深的小孩\N{\fs16}Neither. A babe in the woods.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.82,0:30:24.02,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我景仰她的父亲 - 的确\N{\fs16}- I admired her father. - Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.06,0:30:26.16,正文,,0,0,0,,奈德・史塔克有很多景仰者\N{\fs16}Ned Stark had many admirers,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.19,0:30:27.63,正文,,0,0,0,,又有多少人挺身而出\N{\fs16}and how many stepped forward{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.66,0:30:30.23,正文,,0,0,0,,阻止刽子手砍去他的头颅？\N{\fs16}when the executioner came for his head?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.26,0:30:31.83,正文,,0,0,0,,我帮不了史塔克大人\N{\fs16}I could not help Lord Stark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.87,0:30:35.10,正文,,0,0,0,,- 也许我能帮到他的女儿 - 怎么帮？\N{\fs16}- Perhaps I can help his daughter. - How?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.13,0:30:38.60,正文,,0,0,0,,您不是唯一对她感兴趣的人\N{\fs16}You're not the only one who has taken an interest in her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.64,0:30:40.40,正文,,0,0,0,,这不奇怪\N{\fs16}That's hardly surprising.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.44,0:30:42.77,正文,,0,0,0,,她是个美丽的姑娘 家族显赫\N{\fs16}She's a beautiful girl with a famous name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.81,0:30:46.34,正文,,0,0,0,,的确 如果有合适的求婚者 她会是个不错的妻子\N{\fs16}Indeed. She'd make a lovely match for the right suitor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.38,0:30:49.25,正文,,0,0,0,,我感觉您快说到关键点了\N{\fs16}It almost feels as if you're about to arrive at the point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.28,0:30:51.91,正文,,0,0,0,,小指头不会在君临久留\N{\fs16}Littlefinger is not long for the capital.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.95,0:30:53.95,正文,,0,0,0,,我的一个心腹朋友告诉我\N{\fs16}A confidant of mine has told me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:56.88,正文,,0,0,0,,小指头走的时候 会带珊莎・史塔克一起走\N{\fs16}that when he goes, Sansa Stark goes with him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.92,0:30:59.22,正文,,0,0,0,,为什么您要来告诉我这件事？\N{\fs16}And why have you come to me with this matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.25,0:31:03.06,正文,,0,0,0,,小指头生来没有封地 没有财产也没有军队\N{\fs16}Littlefinger was born with no lands, no wealth, no armies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.09,0:31:04.83,正文,,0,0,0,,现在他已经买到了头两样\N{\fs16}He has acquired the first two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.86,0:31:06.59,正文,,0,0,0,,还需要多久他就能拥有军队？\N{\fs16}How long before he has the army?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.63,0:31:08.73,正文,,0,0,0,,也许您会笑我\N{\fs16}Perhaps you'll laugh,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.76,0:31:10.80,正文,,0,0,0,,但我比大多数人都更了解他\N{\fs16}but I know him better than most{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.83,0:31:13.03,正文,,0,0,0,,这是事实\N{\fs16}and this is the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.07,0:31:17.67,正文,,0,0,0,,小指头是维斯特洛最危险的人之一\N{\fs16}Littlefinger is one of the most dangerous men in Westeros.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.70,0:31:20.07,正文,,0,0,0,,如果罗柏・史塔克失势\N{\fs16}If Robb Stark falls,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.11,0:31:22.51,正文,,0,0,0,,珊莎・史塔克就是北境的钥匙\N{\fs16}Sansa Stark is the key to the North.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.54,0:31:25.51,正文,,0,0,0,,如果小指头娶了她 就等于拿到了这把钥匙\N{\fs16}And if Littlefinger marries her, he'll have the key in his pocket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.54,0:31:27.31,正文,,0,0,0,,这可真是让人羞愧\N{\fs16}Which seems such a shame.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.35,0:31:29.45,正文,,0,0,0,,一个声誉如此之差的人怎么能\N{\fs16}Why should a man with such a low reputation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.48,0:31:31.45,正文,,0,0,0,,抢走这样一位美丽的新娘？\N{\fs16}steal away such a lovely bride?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.48,0:31:33.55,正文,,0,0,0,,你一定很瞧不起他\N{\fs16}You must despise him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.58,0:31:35.72,正文,,0,0,0,,才费了这么多口舌来贬低他\N{\fs16}You're working so hard to undermine him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.75,0:31:38.69,正文,,0,0,0,,实际上 我很欣赏他\N{\fs16}Actually, I rather enjoy him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.72,0:31:40.82,正文,,0,0,0,,可是 只要能当上哪怕一个灰烬之王\N{\fs16}But he would see this country burn{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.86,0:31:43.26,正文,,0,0,0,,他甚至不惜坐视整个王国被付之一炬\N{\fs16}if he could be king of the ashes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.29,0:31:45.33,正文,,0,0,0,,你是个聪明人 瓦里斯大人\N{\fs16}You are a clever man, Lord Varys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.36,0:31:46.89,正文,,0,0,0,,您过奖了\N{\fs16}You are too kind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.93,0:31:49.86,正文,,0,0,0,,我倒是有个可行的方案\N{\fs16}I believe I have a possible solution.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.90,0:31:51.66,正文,,0,0,0,,用不着像你这么聪明也能想到\N{\fs16}One doesn't need to be clever for that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.70,0:31:53.27,正文,,0,0,0,,这都明摆着 不是吗？\N{\fs16}It's all rather obvious, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.71,0:32:06.44,正文,,0,0,0,,咳咳\N{\fs16}Ahem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.48,0:32:08.51,正文,,0,0,0,,我不是故意打扰你的\N{\fs16}I didn't mean to disturb you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.71,0:32:09.51,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(469.469,170.025)}{\pos(80,310)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}珊莎・史塔克{\b0}\N{\fs12}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.55,0:32:10.28,正文,,0,0,0,,你没有打扰\N{\fs16}You haven't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.31,0:32:12.08,正文,,0,0,0,,不介意的话 请到城堡里等着\N{\fs16}We'd like some privacy, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.11,0:32:14.32,正文,,0,0,0,,我们想私下里谈谈\N{\fs16}If you wouldn't mind waiting back inside the keep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.88,0:32:18.75,正文,,0,0,0,,或者告诉我你们的名字\N{\fs16}Or if you'd be kind enough to give me your names,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.79,0:32:21.69,正文,,0,0,0,,我会让国王亲自来跟你们说\N{\fs16}I'll ask the king to speak with you himself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.69,0:32:27.39,正文,,0,0,0,,你在祈祷什么？\N{\fs16}What did you pray for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.43,0:32:30.06,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我不能告诉你 - 为什么？\N{\fs16}- I can't tell you. - Why not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.10,0:32:32.80,正文,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你今早我在圣堂祈祷了什么\N{\fs16}I'll tell you what I prayed for in the sept this morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.83,0:32:36.63,正文,,0,0,0,,我想想 我祈祷我的家族幸福安康\N{\fs16}Let's see, for my family's health and happiness,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.67,0:32:39.90,正文,,0,0,0,,战争划上句点 冬天早日结束\N{\fs16}for an end to the war, for a short winter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.94,0:32:42.57,正文,,0,0,0,,恐怕很无聊 很老套\N{\fs16}Boring and traditional, I'm afraid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.61,0:32:46.41,正文,,0,0,0,,- 你呢？ - 抱歉 我不能说\N{\fs16}- And you? - I'm sorry, I just can't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.44,0:32:48.01,正文,,0,0,0,,我的表姐阿莱娜\N{\fs16}My cousin Alanna{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.04,0:32:50.58,正文,,0,0,0,,是我见过最美的女孩\N{\fs16}was the most beautiful girl I'd ever seen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.61,0:32:52.75,正文,,0,0,0,,我12岁时 经常摔得青一块紫一块\N{\fs16}When I was 12, I was all elbows and knees{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.78,0:32:55.25,正文,,0,0,0,,阿莱娜就像是上天派来折磨我的女神\N{\fs16}and Alanna looked like a goddess sent to torture me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.28,0:32:57.08,正文,,0,0,0,,她叫我猪脸\N{\fs16}Pig-face, she called me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.12,0:32:58.99,正文,,0,0,0,,猪脸？这真荒唐\N{\fs16}Pig-face? That's ridiculous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.02,0:33:01.26,正文,,0,0,0,,我想是因为我的鼻子\N{\fs16}I think it had something to do with my nose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:03.69,正文,,0,0,0,,她只要在大厅里见到我 就会学猪叫\N{\fs16}Whenever she passed me in the halls, she'd oink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.76,0:33:09.56,正文,,0,0,0,,所以我祈祷她会染上可怕的皮肤病\N{\fs16}So I prayed that she'd catch a horrible skin disease.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.60,0:33:12.03,正文,,0,0,0,,一周后 她得了粥斑病\N{\fs16}A week after that, she came down with porridge plague.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.07,0:33:14.67,正文,,0,0,0,,- 粥斑病？ - 你们北境没有吗？\N{\fs16}- Porridge plague? - You don't have it in the North?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.70,0:33:17.10,正文,,0,0,0,,皮肤开始时像煮开了的燕麦片\N{\fs16}Your skin starts to look like boiled oats{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.14,0:33:19.94,正文,,0,0,0,,最后脸部脱落 在痛苦中死去\N{\fs16}and eventually your face slides off and you diein agony.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.97,0:33:21.87,正文,,0,0,0,,这太可怕了\N{\fs16}But that's awful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.08,0:33:26.61,正文,,0,0,0,,你――\N{\fs16}You're--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.64,0:33:28.61,正文,,0,0,0,,我居然相信了你！\N{\fs16}I believed you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.65,0:33:30.55,正文,,0,0,0,,粥斑病 我是个白痴\N{\fs16}Porridge plague. I'm an idiot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.58,0:33:32.78,正文,,0,0,0,,你不是的 别这么说\N{\fs16}Don't say that. No, you're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.82,0:33:35.42,正文,,0,0,0,,阿莱娜后来怎样了？\N{\fs16}So what happened to Alanna?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.45,0:33:37.55,正文,,0,0,0,,她长大后成为最美丽的女子\N{\fs16}Oh, she grew up to be the most beautiful woman{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.59,0:33:40.52,正文,,0,0,0,,嫁给了一位英俊的大人 有了心爱的孩子们\N{\fs16}and married a handsome lord and they have darling children{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.56,0:33:42.36,正文,,0,0,0,,住在海边的城堡里\N{\fs16}and live in a castle by the sea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.39,0:33:44.99,正文,,0,0,0,,真让人沮丧\N{\fs16}It's all terribly frustrating.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.03,0:33:47.73,正文,,0,0,0,,她现在一定很嫉妒你\N{\fs16}I'm sure she's jealous of you now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.76,0:33:50.03,正文,,0,0,0,,你嫁到君临来\N{\fs16}You'll be married here in the capital{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.06,0:33:53.73,正文,,0,0,0,,她会来看你 为你成为王后而假装高兴\N{\fs16}and she'll have to come watch and pretend to be happy that you're queen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.54,0:34:00.31,正文,,0,0,0,,我希望和你成为朋友 好朋友\N{\fs16}I want us to be friends, good friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.34,0:34:02.54,正文,,0,0,0,,我会非常高兴的\N{\fs16}That would make me very happy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.18,0:34:06.01,正文,,0,0,0,,你一定要到高庭来\N{\fs16}You must see Highgarden.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.04,0:34:08.08,正文,,0,0,0,,你会喜欢那儿的 我知道你一定会的\N{\fs16}You'd love it there. I know you would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.11,0:34:11.01,正文,,0,0,0,,我们会在丰收月晚上举行盛大的化妆舞会\N{\fs16}We have a great masquerade the night of the harvest moon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.05,0:34:12.48,正文,,0,0,0,,你一定要来看看戏服\N{\fs16}You should see the costumes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.52,0:34:14.22,正文,,0,0,0,,人们制作了好几个月\N{\fs16}People work on them for months.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.39,0:34:17.69,正文,,0,0,0,,我――我不认为王后\N{\fs16}I-- I don't think the queen{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.72,0:34:19.22,正文,,0,0,0,,会允许我离开君临\N{\fs16}would let me leave King's Landing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.26,0:34:21.06,正文,,0,0,0,,你是指摄政太后吧\N{\fs16}The Queen Regent, you mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.09,0:34:23.46,正文,,0,0,0,,等我嫁给乔佛里 我就会成为王后\N{\fs16}Once I marry Joffrey, I'll be queen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.26,0:34:29.56,正文,,0,0,0,,然后 如果你嫁给洛拉斯……\N{\fs16}And if you were to marry Loras...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.97,0:34:35.77,正文,,0,0,0,,你就会呆在高庭 不是吗？\N{\fs16}Oh, your place would be at Highgarden, wouldn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.80,0:34:39.17,正文,,0,0,0,,我们就是姐妹了\N{\fs16}We would be sisters, you and I.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.21,0:34:41.14,正文,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这提议吗？\N{\fs16}Would you like that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.99,0:34:57.62,正文,,0,0,0,,他叫巴棱\N{\fs16}His name was Bannen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.21,0:35:01.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(297.285,221.75)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}杰奥・莫尔蒙{\b0}\N{\fs12}“熊老” 守夜人总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.65,0:34:59.36,正文,,0,0,0,,他是个好人\N{\fs16}He was a good man,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.39,0:35:01.32,正文,,0,0,0,,优秀的游骑兵\N{\fs16}a good ranger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.36,0:35:03.49,正文,,0,0,0,,他来自……\N{\fs16}He came to us from--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.06,0:35:07.13,正文,,0,0,0,,他是哪儿人？\N{\fs16}where did he come from?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:09.90,正文,,0,0,0,,白港\N{\fs16}Down White Harbor way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.93,0:35:12.07,正文,,0,0,0,,他从白港来到我们中间\N{\fs16}He came to us from White Harbor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.10,0:35:15.14,正文,,0,0,0,,恪尽职守\N{\fs16}Never failed in his duty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.17,0:35:18.27,正文,,0,0,0,,全力谨遵誓言\N{\fs16}He kept his vows the best he could.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.31,0:35:22.21,正文,,0,0,0,,他一马当前 奋勇作战\N{\fs16}He rode far, fought fiercely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.31,0:35:26.75,正文,,0,0,0,,我们将难得再见如此之人\N{\fs16}We shall never see his like again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.78,0:35:30.22,正文,,0,0,0,,他的守望至死方休 于斯结束\N{\fs16}And now his watch has ended.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.48,0:35:34.02,正文,,0,0,0,,他的守望至死方休 于斯结束\N{\fs16}And now his watch has ended.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.36,0:35:41.62,正文,,0,0,0,,没想到区区脚伤也会要了他的命\N{\fs16}Didn't think a broke foot could kill a man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.66,0:35:44.53,正文,,0,0,0,,脚伤可弄不死他\N{\fs16}It wasn't his foot that killed him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.56,0:35:47.23,正文,,0,0,0,,是卡斯特那杂种把他给活活饿死了\N{\fs16}That bastard Craster starved him to death.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.26,0:35:49.06,正文,,0,0,0,,卡斯特得养自己的女儿\N{\fs16}Craster's got his daughters to feed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.10,0:35:50.50,正文,,0,0,0,,你还帮他说话？\N{\fs16}You on his side?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.53,0:35:53.60,正文,,0,0,0,,我们不能打个招呼 就把他的食物偷走\N{\fs16}We can't just show up and steal all his food.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.64,0:35:56.27,正文,,0,0,0,,我们是守夜人 不是贼\N{\fs16}We're brothers of the Night's Watch, not thieves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.30,0:35:58.11,正文,,0,0,0,,我们离开那天\N{\fs16}The day we leave,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.17,0:36:01.74,正文,,0,0,0,,卡斯特肯定会开一瓶好酒\N{\fs16}Craster will tap a barrel of our wine{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.78,0:36:04.91,正文,,0,0,0,,摆上一桌火腿土豆筵席大吃一顿\N{\fs16}and sit down to a feast of ham and potatoes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.95,0:36:06.91,正文,,0,0,0,,然后嘲笑我们\N{\fs16}and laugh at us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.95,0:36:09.18,正文,,0,0,0,,在冰天雪地里挨饿受冻\N{\fs16}starving in the snow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.95,0:36:13.89,正文,,0,0,0,,他是个该死的野人\N{\fs16}He's a bloody wildling is all he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.62,0:36:19.93,正文,,0,0,0,,我没想到巴棱也能烤得这么香\N{\fs16}Never knew Bannen could smell so good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.21,0:36:33.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(208.763,247.104)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}卡斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}野人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.50,0:36:34.07,正文,,0,0,0,,莫尔蒙 你有个儿子吧\N{\fs16}You have one son, don't you, Mormont?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.64,0:36:37.84,正文,,0,0,0,,我有99个儿子\N{\fs16}I had my 99th.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.04,0:36:42.01,正文,,0,0,0,,你还没见过哪个老子有99个儿子吧？\N{\fs16}You ever meet a man with 99 sons?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.78,0:36:47.28,正文,,0,0,0,,我女儿多得数不过来\N{\fs16}And more daughters than I can count.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.32,0:36:49.72,正文,,0,0,0,,我真为你高兴 呵呵 真的？\N{\fs16}- I'm glad for you. - Are you now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.75,0:36:53.42,正文,,0,0,0,,我可希望你和你的崽子们早点滚蛋\N{\fs16}Me, I'll be glad when you and yours have gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:55.52,正文,,0,0,0,,等伤兵再恢复些我们就离开\N{\fs16}As soon as our wounded are strong enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.56,0:36:57.49,正文,,0,0,0,,唉\N{\fs16}Ah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.53,0:36:59.63,正文,,0,0,0,,他们这样已经算不错了\N{\fs16}They're as strong as they're gonna get.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.53,0:37:02.93,正文,,0,0,0,,那些只剩一口气的\N{\fs16}Them that's dying,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.96,0:37:05.06,正文,,0,0,0,,怎么不直接给喉咙上开道口子了结算了？\N{\fs16}why don't you cut their throats and be done with it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.10,0:37:07.07,正文,,0,0,0,,啊？\N{\fs16}Hmm?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.10,0:37:10.30,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你不想的话 可以留给我\N{\fs16}Or leave them if you've not the stomach{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:11.87,正文,,0,0,0,,我来帮你代劳\N{\fs16}and I'll sort them myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.21,0:37:16.07,正文,,0,0,0,,你要了结了谁啊 老头子？\N{\fs16}Whose throat you gonna cut, old man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.51,0:37:20.84,正文,,0,0,0,,给我出去等着\N{\fs16}Wait outside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.88,0:37:24.28,正文,,0,0,0,,外边太冷了 一丁点吃的都没有\N{\fs16}It's cold outside and there's nothing to eat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.32,0:37:25.82,正文,,0,0,0,,我老婆给过你们面包了\N{\fs16}My wives gave you bread.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.85,0:37:29.09,正文,,0,0,0,,面包里满是木屑\N{\fs16}There's sawdust in the bread.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.12,0:37:30.65,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你不喜欢\N{\fs16}You don't like it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.69,0:37:33.06,正文,,0,0,0,,你可以出去找点雪吃\N{\fs16}you go out there and eat the snow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.96,0:37:41.80,正文,,0,0,0,,我只想吃你藏起来的好东西\N{\fs16}I'd rather eat what you've got hidden away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.90,0:37:46.87,正文,,0,0,0,,我说了 出去等着\N{\fs16}I told you to wait outside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.90,0:37:48.73,正文,,0,0,0,,他现在坐在这儿喝我们的酒\N{\fs16}He's sitting there drinking our wine,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.77,0:37:50.47,正文,,0,0,0,,得等我们死了才会享用他屯的好东西\N{\fs16}eating his fill while we die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.64,0:37:54.14,正文,,0,0,0,,我已经给你们这些乌鸦够多了\N{\fs16}I gave you crows enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.17,0:37:55.44,正文,,0,0,0,,我得喂饱我的女人们！\N{\fs16}I've got to feed my women!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.47,0:37:57.37,正文,,0,0,0,,你这是承认自己把好东西都藏起来了？\N{\fs16}So you admit you've got a hidden larder, then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.41,0:37:58.89,正文,,0,0,0,,否则你怎么过冬？\N{\fs16}How else'd you make it through winter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.91,0:38:01.91,正文,,0,0,0,,够了！滚出去！\N{\fs16}Enough! Out!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.95,0:38:03.81,正文,,0,0,0,,我可是个敬神的人\N{\fs16}I am a godly man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.85,0:38:05.35,正文,,0,0,0,,你是个吝啬的杂种！\N{\fs16}You're a stingy bastard!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.38,0:38:06.75,正文,,0,0,0,,杂种？\N{\fs16}Bastard?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.78,0:38:10.29,正文,,0,0,0,,我跟你这小贼出去说话！\N{\fs16}Out with you, you little thief.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.32,0:38:13.69,正文,,0,0,0,,还有你！和你！\N{\fs16}And you! And you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.43,0:38:17.96,正文,,0,0,0,,都给我滚到雪地里饿肚子去\N{\fs16}Go sleep in the cold on empty bellies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.33,0:38:22.10,正文,,0,0,0,,谁再敢说我是杂种\N{\fs16}I'll chop the hands off the next man{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.13,0:38:24.47,正文,,0,0,0,,我就把他的手砍下来\N{\fs16}who calls me bastard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.55,0:38:41.18,正文,,0,0,0,,你就是个杂种\N{\fs16}You are a bastard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.85,0:38:47.35,正文,,0,0,0,,操女儿的野人 该死的杂种\N{\fs16}A daughter-fucking, wildling bastard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.23,0:38:57.16,正文,,0,0,0,,诸神会为此诅咒我们的\N{\fs16}The gods will curse us for this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.19,0:38:58.52,正文,,0,0,0,,诸神的律法将――\N{\fs16}By all the laws--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.54,0:39:00.42,正文,,0,0,0,,长城之外 没有律法\N{\fs16}There are no laws beyond the Wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.56,0:39:02.10,正文,,0,0,0,,告诉我们他把那些好东西都藏在哪儿了\N{\fs16}Now show us where he hides the food{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.13,0:39:04.23,正文,,0,0,0,,否则你的下场就和他一样\N{\fs16}or you'll get the same as he did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.27,0:39:06.67,正文,,0,0,0,,放开她\N{\fs16}Unhand her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.70,0:39:08.57,正文,,0,0,0,,我要砍了你的头\N{\fs16}I shall have your head for this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.01,0:40:02.38,正文,,0,0,0,,- 赶紧 赶紧 - 发生了什么？\N{\fs16}- Quickly. Quickly. - What's happening?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.42,0:40:05.98,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我可不敢出去 - 不 我们必须逃跑 快逃！\N{\fs16}- I'm not going out there. - No, we have to go. Now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:13.69,正文,,0,0,0,,跟我来 我知道小路捷径\N{\fs16}Follow me. I know the best way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.53,0:40:17.43,正文,,0,0,0,,走这边\N{\fs16}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.07,0:40:25.00,正文,,0,0,0,,猪崽儿 跑快点\N{\fs16}Run fast, Piggy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.03,0:40:27.34,正文,,0,0,0,,睡好！\N{\fs16}and sleep well!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.37,0:40:30.31,正文,,0,0,0,,到时候我就来解决你\N{\fs16}I'll be cutting your throat one of these nights.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.61,0:40:37.14,正文,,0,0,0,,能帮我把这头罩摘下来了吗？\N{\fs16}Can I take this hood off yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.18,0:40:38.91,正文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 小姐\N{\fs16}I do apologize, little lady,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.95,0:40:41.65,正文,,0,0,0,,但你还是不知道我们去哪儿的好\N{\fs16}but it's better for you if you don't see where we're going.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.02,0:40:49.15,正文,,0,0,0,,停下！\N{\fs16}Halt!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.59,0:40:57.06,正文,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么？ - 黑带朗姆酒\N{\fs16}- What is it? - Blackstrap rum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.51,0:40:58.71,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(101.857,233.43)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}密尔的索罗斯{\b0}\N{\fs12}无旗兄弟会的红袍僧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.93,0:40:59.60,正文,,0,0,0,,啊！\N{\fs16}Ugh!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.63,0:41:01.90,正文,,0,0,0,,要在战争时期找点安慰可不容易\N{\fs16}Not easy finding molasses in wartime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.93,0:41:03.80,正文,,0,0,0,,我也来点\N{\fs16}I'd have some.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.01,0:41:05.71,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(120.948,213.698)}{\pos(180,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}安盖{\b0}\N{\fs12}“射手” 来自风暴地的弓箭手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.37,0:41:08.80,正文,,0,0,0,,我们回家了\N{\fs16}Let's go home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:27.58,正文,,0,0,0,,这是哪儿？\N{\fs16}What is this place?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.62,0:41:30.72,正文,,0,0,0,,狼和狮子都找不到的地方\N{\fs16}Somewhere neither wolves nor lions come prowling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.71,0:41:30.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(352.607,248.849)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}艾莉亚・史塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.71,0:41:30.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(487.881,250.278)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}詹德利{\b0}\N{\fs12}“大牛” 铁匠学徒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.21,0:41:41.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(532.257,222.597)}{\pos(180,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}桑铎・克里冈{\b0}\N{\fs12}“猎狗”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.70,0:41:42.50,正文,,0,0,0,,你们看着就像群猪倌\N{\fs16}You look like a bunch of swineherds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.53,0:41:44.57,正文,,0,0,0,,我们中的确有些猪倌\N{\fs16}Some of us were swineherds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.60,0:41:47.27,正文,,0,0,0,,还有些皮革工和石匠\N{\fs16}And some of us tanners and masons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.30,0:41:48.67,正文,,0,0,0,,那都是过去的事了\N{\fs16}That was before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.70,0:41:50.64,正文,,0,0,0,,你们仍旧是猪倌\N{\fs16}You're still swineherds{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.67,0:41:53.57,正文,,0,0,0,,皮革工和石匠\N{\fs16}and tanners and masons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.61,0:41:56.61,正文,,0,0,0,,拿把破矛就能当战士了？\N{\fs16}You think carrying a crooked spear makes you a soldier?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.65,0:41:59.85,正文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs16}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.88,0:42:03.18,正文,,0,0,0,,战争才能铸就真正的战士\N{\fs16}Fighting in a war makes you a soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.22,0:42:05.25,正文,,0,0,0,,贝里・唐德利恩？\N{\fs16}Beric Dondarrion?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.29,0:42:06.99,正文,,0,0,0,,你有过好日子 如今落到这般田地\N{\fs16}You've seen better days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.41,0:42:09.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(516.995,255.05)}{\pos(180,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}贝里・唐德利恩{\b0}\N{\fs12}“闪电大王” 无旗兄弟会的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.02,0:42:09.55,正文,,0,0,0,,好日子一去不复返了\N{\fs16}And I won't see them again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.96,0:42:12.96,正文,,0,0,0,,史塔克的逃兵\N{\fs16}Stark deserters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.99,0:42:15.59,正文,,0,0,0,,拜拉席恩的逃兵\N{\fs16}Baratheon deserters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.63,0:42:17.19,正文,,0,0,0,,你们才不是参加战争\N{\fs16}You lot aren't fighting in a war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.23,0:42:18.73,正文,,0,0,0,,你们是战场的逃兵\N{\fs16}You're running from it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.76,0:42:21.06,正文,,0,0,0,,我上次听到你的消息 你还是乔佛里国王的忠狗\N{\fs16}Last I heard, you were King Joffrey's guard dog.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.10,0:42:24.97,正文,,0,0,0,,可你如今千里迢迢赶到这儿\N{\fs16}But here you are 1,000 miles from home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.00,0:42:26.70,正文,,0,0,0,,咱俩谁是逃兵呢？\N{\fs16}Which of us is running?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.74,0:42:28.80,正文,,0,0,0,,解开绳子我们就知道了\N{\fs16}Untie these ropes and we'll find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.84,0:42:32.54,正文,,0,0,0,,你躲这儿带着帮农民想做什么？\N{\fs16}What are you doing leading a mob of peasants?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.58,0:42:35.38,正文,,0,0,0,,奈德・史塔克让我杀了你兄弟\N{\fs16}Ned Stark ordered me to execute your brother{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.41,0:42:36.71,正文,,0,0,0,,以劳勃国王之名\N{\fs16}in King Robert's name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.75,0:42:39.21,正文,,0,0,0,,奈德・史塔克早死了\N{\fs16}Ned Stark is dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.25,0:42:41.48,正文,,0,0,0,,劳勃国王也躺在坟墓里头\N{\fs16}King Robert is dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.52,0:42:43.72,正文,,0,0,0,,我兄弟可还活得好好的\N{\fs16}My brother's alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.05,0:42:47.92,正文,,0,0,0,,你们这是为了死人而战\N{\fs16}You're fighting for ghosts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.96,0:42:49.82,正文,,0,0,0,,我们就是孤魂野鬼――\N{\fs16}That's what we are--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.86,0:42:53.69,正文,,0,0,0,,在黑暗中等待你大驾光临\N{\fs16}ghosts waiting for you in the dark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.73,0:42:56.09,正文,,0,0,0,,你看不见我们\N{\fs16}You can't see us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.13,0:42:58.06,正文,,0,0,0,,但我们能看见你\N{\fs16}but we see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.10,0:43:00.37,正文,,0,0,0,,无论你身穿哪家战袍――\N{\fs16}No matter whose cloak you wear--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.40,0:43:03.03,正文,,0,0,0,,兰尼斯特 史塔克 拜拉席恩――\N{\fs16}Lannister, Stark, Baratheon--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.07,0:43:05.07,正文,,0,0,0,,你要是对弱者下手\N{\fs16}you prey on the weak,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.10,0:43:07.94,正文,,0,0,0,,无旗兄弟会便会将你拿下\N{\fs16}the Brotherhood without Banners will hunt you down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.97,0:43:10.01,正文,,0,0,0,,你找到了神？当真？\N{\fs16}You found god? Is that it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.04,0:43:12.68,正文,,0,0,0,,没错 我在世间唯一真神的光里\N{\fs16}Aye. I've been reborn{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.71,0:43:14.68,正文,,0,0,0,,获得了重生\N{\fs16}in the light of the one true god.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.51,0:43:17.21,正文,,0,0,0,,我们都是如此\N{\fs16}As have we all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.25,0:43:19.75,正文,,0,0,0,,世间有此经历的人都会如此\N{\fs16}As would any man who's seen the things we've seen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.78,0:43:22.48,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你想杀了我 他妈的赶紧动手\N{\fs16}If you mean to murder me, then bloody well get on with it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.52,0:43:25.69,正文,,0,0,0,,你迟早会死 狗\N{\fs16}You'll die soon enough, dog.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.72,0:43:29.26,正文,,0,0,0,,非为谋杀 只为正义\N{\fs16}But it won't be murder, only justice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.29,0:43:31.23,正文,,0,0,0,,这比你应得的要慷慨多了\N{\fs16}And a kinder fate than you deserve.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.26,0:43:32.76,正文,,0,0,0,,你们总自称是狮子\N{\fs16}Lions you call yourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.79,0:43:36.00,正文,,0,0,0,,戏子滩上 你们强奸了七岁的小女孩\N{\fs16}At the Mummer's Ford, girls of seven years were raped{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.03,0:43:38.26,正文,,0,0,0,,喂奶的母亲\N{\fs16}and babes still on the breast{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.30,0:43:39.97,正文,,0,0,0,,眼睁睁地看着自己的儿女被切成两半\N{\fs16}were cut in two while their mothers watched.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.00,0:43:42.27,正文,,0,0,0,,我那时不在戏子滩\N{\fs16}I wasn't at the Mummer's Ford.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.30,0:43:44.80,正文,,0,0,0,,别把这笔烂帐算到我头上\N{\fs16}Dump your dead children at some other door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.84,0:43:47.20,正文,,0,0,0,,克里冈家族就是构筑在死婴之上的\N{\fs16}House Clegane was built upon dead children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.24,0:43:49.77,正文,,0,0,0,,我亲眼目睹他们将伊耿王子和雷妮丝公主的尸体\N{\fs16}I saw them lay Prince Aegon and Princess Rhaenys{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.81,0:43:51.34,正文,,0,0,0,,陈放在铁王座前\N{\fs16}before the Iron Throne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.38,0:43:53.11,正文,,0,0,0,,你以为我跟我老哥一样？\N{\fs16}Do you take me for my brother?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.14,0:43:55.61,正文,,0,0,0,,生于克里冈家就是罪名？\N{\fs16}Is being born Clegane a crime?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.65,0:43:58.68,正文,,0,0,0,,- 谋杀是罪名 - 我可没碰过坦格利安的崽子们\N{\fs16}- Murder is a crime. - I never touched the Targaryen babes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.71,0:44:01.52,正文,,0,0,0,,从没见过 连闻都没闻过\N{\fs16}I never saw them, never smelled them,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.55,0:44:03.42,正文,,0,0,0,,连他们的哭啼声都没听过\N{\fs16}never heard them bawling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.45,0:44:07.12,正文,,0,0,0,,你想杀了我 那就赶紧来！\N{\fs16}You want to cut my throat, get on with it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.16,0:44:09.19,正文,,0,0,0,,别把杀人者的名头扣在我头上\N{\fs16}But don't call me murderer{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.23,0:44:11.06,正文,,0,0,0,,然后自己假装不是\N{\fs16}and pretend that you're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.09,0:44:13.13,正文,,0,0,0,,你杀了米凯\N{\fs16}You murdered Mycah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.16,0:44:14.66,正文,,0,0,0,,屠夫家的儿子\N{\fs16}The butcher's boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.70,0:44:16.63,正文,,0,0,0,,我的好朋友\N{\fs16}My friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.67,0:44:19.90,正文,,0,0,0,,他才12岁 手无寸铁\N{\fs16}He was 12 years old. He was unarmed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.93,0:44:21.30,正文,,0,0,0,,你骑马追杀他\N{\fs16}And you rode him down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.34,0:44:24.04,正文,,0,0,0,,你把他的尸体挂在马背上 就像是你猎杀的一头鹿\N{\fs16}You slung him over your horse like he was some deer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.07,0:44:26.64,正文,,0,0,0,,唉 我才碰碰他就往外冒血\N{\fs16}Aye, he was a bleeder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.81,0:44:29.37,正文,,0,0,0,,你并不否认你杀了那个孩子？\N{\fs16}You don't deny killing this boy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.41,0:44:31.04,正文,,0,0,0,,我是乔佛里的贴身侍卫\N{\fs16}I was Joffrey's sworn shield.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.08,0:44:33.08,正文,,0,0,0,,- 那孩子袭击王子 - 你说谎！\N{\fs16}- The boy attacked the prince. - That's a lie!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.11,0:44:36.52,正文,,0,0,0,,是我打伤了乔佛里 米凯逃走了\N{\fs16}I hit Joffrey. Mycah just ran away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.55,0:44:38.18,正文,,0,0,0,,那我应该杀了你\N{\fs16}Then I should have killed you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.22,0:44:41.42,正文,,0,0,0,,我没资格质疑王子\N{\fs16}Not my place to question princes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.92,0:44:44.92,正文,,0,0,0,,你被控谋杀\N{\fs16}You stand accused of murder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.96,0:44:47.29,正文,,0,0,0,,但此处没人知道指控的真假\N{\fs16}But no one here knows the truth of the charge,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.33,0:44:49.66,正文,,0,0,0,,所以我们无法裁定\N{\fs16}so it is not for us to judge you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.69,0:44:52.50,正文,,0,0,0,,只有光之王才能审判你\N{\fs16}Only the Lord of Light may do that now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.50,0:44:57.17,正文,,0,0,0,,我决定进行比武审判\N{\fs16}I sentence you to trial by combat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.24,0:45:01.64,正文,,0,0,0,,那么 你们谁上呢？\N{\fs16}So, who will it be?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.84,0:45:04.57,正文,,0,0,0,,我们来看看你的火神究竟\N{\fs16}Should we find out if your fire god{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.61,0:45:06.91,正文,,0,0,0,,爱不爱你 牧师先生？\N{\fs16}really loves you, priest?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.94,0:45:08.44,正文,,0,0,0,,或者是你 弓箭手？\N{\fs16}Or you, archer?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.47,0:45:10.69,正文,,0,0,0,,我很想见识一下你的剑法哟？\N{\fs16}What are you worth with a sword in your hand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.95,0:45:14.51,正文,,0,0,0,,还是我们最勇敢的小丫头呢？\N{\fs16}Or is the little girl the bravest one here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.65,0:45:18.62,正文,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs16}Aye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.65,0:45:20.72,正文,,0,0,0,,她的确勇敢\N{\fs16}She might be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.82,0:45:24.89,正文,,0,0,0,,但你的对手是我\N{\fs16}But it's me you'll fight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.21,0:45:37.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(399.776,289.63)}{\pos(280,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}丹妮莉丝・坦格利安{\b0}\N{\fs12}风暴降生 龙之母
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.61,0:45:48.71,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(485.475,225.391)}{\pos(50,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}克拉兹尼・莫・纳克罗兹{\b0}\N{\fs12}阿斯塔波的奴隶主
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.61,0:45:48.71,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(120.882,229.576)}{\pos(50,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}格雷赞\N{\b0}{\fs12}阿斯塔波的奴隶主
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.61,0:45:51.12,正文,,0,0,0,,主人说他们还未经考验\N{\fs16}The master says they are untested.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.38,0:45:57.32,正文,,0,0,0,,他说最好先让他们接受血的试练\N{\fs16}He says you would be wise to blood them early.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.35,0:45:59.96,正文,,0,0,0,,这儿周边有许多小城市\N{\fs16}There are many small cities between here and there,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.99,0:46:02.09,正文,,0,0,0,,这些城市有丰富的资源\N{\fs16}cities ripe for sacking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.03,0:46:06.06,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你抓到了俘虏\N{\fs16}Should you take captives,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.10,0:46:09.26,正文,,0,0,0,,贤主们可以高价收购健康的战俘\N{\fs16}the masters will buy the healthy ones and for a good price.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.03,0:46:15.34,正文,,0,0,0,,世事难料\N{\fs16}And who knows?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.37,0:46:19.47,正文,,0,0,0,,10年后你送来的某些男孩子\N{\fs16}In 10 years, some of the boys you send them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.51,0:46:21.71,正文,,0,0,0,,也许也会成为无垢者\N{\fs16}may be Unsullied in their turn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.21,0:46:24.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(466.732,308.354)}{\pos(50,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}弥桑黛{\b0}\N{\fs12}奴隶翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.74,0:46:23.88,正文,,0,0,0,,这对我们都有利\N{\fs16}Thus all shall prosper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.21,0:46:33.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(414.089,265.506)}{\pos(150,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}乔拉・莫尔蒙{\b0}\N{\fs12}“大熊” 熊老之子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.21,0:46:33.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(202.558,265.738)}{\pos(273,272)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}巴利斯坦・赛尔弥\N{\fs12}“无畏的” 女王铁卫
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.21,0:46:47.21,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(202.558,265.738)}{\pos(273,272)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}卓耿\N{\fs12}丹妮莉丝的黑龙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.42,0:47:20.62,正文,,0,0,0,,成交了吗？他们属于我了？\N{\fs16}Is it done, then? They belong to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.01,0:47:24.30,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(321.884,293.014)}成交了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.21,0:47:27.11,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(319.515,294.196)}你握紧这鞭子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.91,0:47:32.14,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(320.7,295.377)}这支军队归你这婊子了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.21,0:47:56.36,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(325.44,294.196)}无垢者！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.31,0:48:05.01,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(325.441,293.014)}向前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.81,0:48:07.91,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(325.441,295.377)}立定！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.31,0:48:17.81,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(320.7,294.196)}这婊子的怪物不听我话啊
